text: IBK Sundsvall was a floorball club in Sundsvall in Sweden. It was established in 1986. The men's team played in the Swedish top division during the 1990's. In 2006 the club merged with IBK Nordic becoming Sundsvall City. In 1991 the club also played soccer in the men's Division 6. ==References== Category:1986 establishments in Sweden Category:2006 disestablishments in Sweden Category:Floorball clubs in Sweden Category:Sundsvall
